{"tid":1239172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（回帶）烏克蘭鎮暴警察 集體下跪求原諒","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:06:20.000Z","uid":120361,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c45addd32c2652ab12990a28d51852a408fae0e9","tid":1239172,"uid":120361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"2014-02-26 07:49<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕外電報導，上週受命與示威者武力對抗的烏克蘭鎮暴警察，昨天部分警員出現在西部城市利沃夫（Lviv），集體下跪請求原諒。<br />\n據報導，這群警察昨天返回家鄉利沃夫時，在台上跪下請求原諒。這群警察強調他們沒有殺害或虐打示威者，仍得不到當地民眾的原諒，更有民眾不斷高呼「羞恥」，宣洩內心不滿。<br />\n<br />\n不過，東部俄語區對亞努科維奇被推翻、親西方派接管政府仍深有疑慮與不滿，23日上萬人示威要求俄羅斯介入，臨時總統圖奇諾夫（Oleksander Turchinov）警告，「烏克蘭部分地區有非常危險的分裂主義跡象」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvMPQkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvMPQkW.png&h=17372144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php7AziWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php7AziWg.jpg&h=55906d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/957881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F957881&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=5c2b8522\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F957881&h=15021d5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/957881</a>"},{"pid":"4f530a0bc61b34e4bcaa2303602c0b7a1635ea46","tid":1239172,"uid":102700,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"我反而唔想黑驚洗白<br />\n繼續黑落去先召喚到更多人"},{"pid":"728b655a096f8a5216fe9dc12395d7ebd7915960","tid":1239172,"uid":120361,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"班香港警察一定唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=